# Expert Consultations Log Directory

This directory contains automatically generated consultation logs from expert sessions.

## Structure
- File naming: `YYYY-MM-DD-[expert-topic]-[session-id].md`
- Content: Question, expert response, action items, integration notes

## Purpose  
- Track expert guidance throughout project development
- Create searchable knowledge base of expert insights
- Enable follow-up and action item tracking
- Provide context for future consultations

## Integration with BMad
Expert consultation insights feed back into:
- Story refinements and new story creation
- Architecture document updates  
- Code quality improvements
- Design direction changes

Each consultation log includes:
- Context of when/why expert was consulted
- Full expert response and recommendations
- Action items extracted from expert advice
- Integration status with BMad workflow